dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.resource.res.log.network.NetworkComposite
dataStructure.description:
This class represents an aggregation of NetworkAtomic and possibly NetworkComposite objects. Each NetworkAtomic object represents a stand-alone Network; these can be combined to build larger Networks by choosing the appropriate type of NetworkComposite object to aggregate NetworkAtomic objects. Note that a NetworkComposite object can also aggregate NetworkComposite objects.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: NetworkComposite
